  "detailed_description": "Step into the relentless chaos of deep space warfare in \"Hyperlight Survivor\", a Competitive Bullet Hell with roguelite mechanics. Brace yourself as you become the ultimate Champion, fighting against an endless horde of enemies determined to destroy your spaceship.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Survive </h2>Pilot your spaceship through a series of ever-changing arena, the longer you survive, the more challenging the battle become!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/13f8b0864e4c40f558b1d07256e4e0c8.poster.avif?t=1700572990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/13f8b0864e4c40f558b1d07256e4e0c8.webm?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/13f8b0864e4c40f558b1d07256e4e0c8.mp4?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rank Up</h2>Complete contracts to reach higher ranks, but if you fail, you will lose your Rank Score and derank!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/67d0b854487d3692f5bbfbabae174aaa.poster.avif?t=1700572990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/67d0b854487d3692f5bbfbabae174aaa.webm?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/67d0b854487d3692f5bbfbabae174aaa.mp4?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unleash Your Arsenal</h2>Unlock new powerful spaceships, each with its own unique playstyle and Ultra. There are no limits to the weapons and Power-Ups you can acquire so enhance your ship and unleash the true power of your arsenal!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/b06036f9407347503f192acdc85be83a.poster.avif?t=1700572990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/b06036f9407347503f192acdc85be83a.webm?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/b06036f9407347503f192acdc85be83a.mp4?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Twist The Arena</h2>Pick a Random Arena Box and watch the battlefield change. Deadly turrets and moving spikes will make your survival more challenging!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/6e7a4109d49ef54c5d89bb8565ea9036.poster.avif?t=1700572990\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/6e7a4109d49ef54c5d89bb8565ea9036.webm?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522940/extras/6e7a4109d49ef54c5d89bb8565ea9036.mp4?t=1700572990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
